WEBVTT

00:02:28.217 --> 00:02:31.713
The few early sharks
lived offshore in fear.

00:02:32.900 --> 00:02:36.652
Your few four-legged ancestors,
the tetrapods,

00:02:36.676 --> 00:02:39.147
struggled in tropical river plains.

00:02:40.391 --> 00:02:42.102
Ecosystems were crowded.

00:02:42.744 --> 00:02:44.599
There was no escape,

00:02:44.623 --> 00:02:46.375
no opportunity in sight.

00:02:47.110 --> 00:02:48.496
Then the world ended.

00:02:48.888 --> 00:02:50.838
(Laughter)

00:02:50.862 --> 00:02:52.227
No, it is a good thing.

00:02:52.251 --> 00:02:56.619
96 percent of all fish species died

00:02:56.643 --> 00:03:01.103
during the Hangenberg event,
359 million years ago: